Chinese: 那里真的没人检测出阳性。
我们有办法让事情运转起来。
但我们所有人都非常健康。

English: Everybody's always negative coming out of Mexico.
I mean, I wasn't sure if they were playing fast and loose with the rules or if really nobody tests positive there.
I'm just saying it was strange.
But we have ways of making things work if they don't work.
But we were all quite well.
All the staff wore face shields plus a mask, which was really kind of sad out there.
Chinese: 而且我理解每个人的负面情绪。
每个人从墨西哥出来时总是持负面态度。
我的意思是，我不确定他们是故意玩弄规则，还是那里真没人检测出阳性。
但如果事情不顺利，我们也有办法让它运作起来。
但我们所有人都非常健康。
所有工作人员都戴了护目镜加上口罩，那在外面真是相当令人难过。

input: And I understand everybody's negative. Everybody's always negative coming out of Mexico. So that's kind of strange. I mean, I wasn't sure if they were playing fast and loose with the rules or if really nobody tests positive there. I don't know why. I'm just saying it was strange. But we have ways of making things work if they don't work. But we were all quite well. All the staff wore face shields plus a mask, which was really kind of sad out there.
